3.10	Persecuted_bandurists	Persecuted bandurists	Many bandurists and kobzars were persecuted by the authorities that controlled Ukraine at various times because of the association of the bandura to the Cossack past and aspects of Ukrainian history which the kobzars would glorify in their songs and epics.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/fd/Pamiatnyk.jpg/200px-Pamiatnyk.jpg
